      {
        "id": "3851995391856658258",
        "type": "Image",
        "shortCode": "DV1CWZwDsdS",
        "caption": "March 13th, 2026 -- 9:19 AM.\nParaskevidekatriaphobia.\n\nNo luck in sight.\n\nA receding hairline.\nHair turning white.\n\nThe struggle became desperation.\n\nDisappointed? No.\nAngry? Yes.\n\nI went from having no mirrors in my office…\nto surrounding myself with them.\n\nI stand there, looking into my own eyes.\n\nVoice: “What the hell are you doing, dude?”\nVoice: “You only lose if you stop.”\nVoice: “How pathetic would it be to quit now?”\n\nIt would be easy to walk away.\nTo drop everything.\n\nBut defeat only happens if I stop.\nSo I keep going.\n\nVelocity. 10 hours a day.\nVelocity. 12 hours a day.\nVelocity. 13 hours a day.\nVelocity. 14 hours a day. \n.. again.. again.. until the heart stops into the next life.\n\nThank you, Ahmed.\nThank you, me.\n\nThank you for believing in me, Ahmed.",
